<section class="faq-section">
    <h1 style="color: #433878;">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>1. What is Wedease?</h2>
        <p>Wedease is an online marketplace dedicated to providing services for weddings in India. We offer a wide range of services such as venues, catering, photography, and more to help make your wedding day special.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>2. How do I register on Wedease?</h2>
        <p>To register on Wedease, simply click on the "Register" button on our homepage. You can choose to register as a user or a vendor. Users can book services, while vendors can list their services for others to book.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>3. What services are available on Wedease?</h2>
        <p style="color: #433878;">Wedease offers a variety of wedding-related services, including:
            <ul>
                <li style="color: #433878;">Venues for the ceremony and reception</li>
                <li style="color: #433878;">Catering services</li>
                <li style="color: #433878;">Photography and videography</li>
                <li style="color: #433878;">Wedding planners</li>
                <li style="color: #433878;">Decor services</li>
                <li style="color: #433878;">And much more!</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="color: #433878;">Visit the "Services" section of our website to explore all our offerings.</p>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>4. How do I book a service on Wedease?</h2>
        <p>To book a service, simply browse through the available categories in the "Services" section. Once you find the service you need, you can contact the vendor directly through their profile or book online, if the option is available.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>5. How do I become a vendor on Wedease?</h2>
        <p>If you're a service provider in the wedding industry, you can register as a vendor on Wedease. Simply go to the "Register as Vendor" page, fill out the registration form, and submit your details. Once approved, you’ll be able to list your services for potential clients.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>6. Can I make changes to my booking?</h2>
        <p>Yes, you can modify your booking by contacting the vendor directly through the platform. Each vendor has different policies regarding booking changes, so make sure to discuss any changes in advance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>7. Is my personal information safe on Wedease?</h2>
        <p>Yes, we take your privacy seriously. All personal data is securely stored and protected. We follow industry best practices to ensure that your information is safe.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>8. How do I contact customer support?</h2>
        <p>You can contact customer support by visiting the "Contact Us" page and filling out the form. We’ll respond to your inquiry as soon as possible. Alternatively, you can reach us via email at support@wedease.com.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>9. How do I get a refund?</h2>
        <p>Refund policies vary by service provider. If you need a refund, please check the specific vendor's cancellation and refund policy. If you're facing issues, contact our customer support team for assistance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>10. Can I leave reviews for vendors?</h2>
        <p>Yes, after booking a service and completing your event, you’ll be able to leave a review for the vendor based on your experience. Your feedback helps other users make informed decisions and supports vendors in improving their services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>11. Is Wedease available in my area?</h2>
        <p>Currently, Wedease operates primarily in select regions of India. You can check the availability of services in your location by browsing the "Services" section or entering your location details.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h2>12. What payment methods are accepted?</h2>
        <p>We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards, net banking, and UPI payments. All payments are securely processed.</p>
    </div>
</section>

